# Novel2Script System Design

## Overview

Novel2Script converts long-form novels into structured screenplay drafts.

The system uses Large Language Models to extract characters, scenes and dialogues.

---

## Workflow

Novel Input

↓

Novel Parsing

↓

Character Extraction

↓

Scene Segmentation

↓

Script Generation

↓

YAML Export

---

## Modules

### Upload Module

Receive novel text.

### Parser Module

Analyze chapter structure.

### Character Module

Extract important characters.

### Scene Module

Split story into scenes.

### Script Generator

Generate screenplay content.

### Export Module

Export YAML file.

